{"tid":630165,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【空襲敘利亞】支那外交部：反對國際關係中使用武力　單邊軍事行動違國際法","createTime":"2018-04-15T10:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T13:36:50.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd1ba0e39f52e175a58d70943b5a30fcd5ce2c72","tid":630165,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T10:47:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【空襲敘利亞】外交部：反對國際關係中使用武力　單邊軍事行動違國際法</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180414/s00004/a426d31dd9327f58f748921d145917b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180414%2Fs00004%2Fa426d31dd9327f58f748921d145917b4.jpg&h=a09584f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美英法三國於敘利亞時間周六（14日）清晨4點，空襲敘利亞化學武器設施和據點，聲言是對當地政府在東古塔杜馬地區發動化武襲擊的回應。中國外交部發言人華春瑩今日傍晚表示，中國反對在國際關係中使用武力，任何繞過聯合國安理會的單邊軍事行動違反國際法原則，敦促有關方面通過對話和協商解決問題。她又指，目前未有中國公民受到襲擊影響。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩指出，中國尊重各國的主權、獨立和領土完整，而任何繞過聯合國安理會的單邊軍事行動違反國際法原則，並為敘利亞的局勢增添新的複雜因素。<br />\n<br />\n對於敘利亞政府被指發動化學武器襲擊，華春瑩稱，各國應對事件進行全面、公正和客觀的調查，在得出可靠結論前可靠前，各方不能預先定斷結果。她又指，中方認為政治解決是敘利亞問題的唯一出路，國際應支持以聯合國作為斡旋渠道，為解決敘利亞問題付出努力。<br />\n<br />\n而中國駐敘利亞大使館馬旭亮參贊表示，是次美國對敘利亞的軍事打擊，使館區域沒受影響，使館人員安全，館舍完好。據使館方面統計，目前在敘中國公民共有83人，在軍事打擊後，使館第一時間聯絡他們，截至目前沒有中國公民傷亡的報告。<br />\n<br />\n（中國外交部網站／澎湃）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180414/s00004/1523700802239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180414%2Fs00004%2F1523700802239&d=wA%2B%2BjXaLGJqe9MEM5ILW5hxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=1511ae08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180414%2Fs00004%2F1523700802239&h=07db519b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180414/s00004/1523700802239</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係到吠"},{"pid":"269f11d0a518c6372cbf5fc4836bca82595ab889","tid":630165,"uid":48,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T10:49:58.000Z","msg":"冇人識佢 係咁扮大佬出黎吠<br />\n<br />\n企開啲啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3de1cf908ab792d84e7158316b61bd7e2701197","tid":630165,"uid":41509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T10:50:09.000Z","msg":"原來支那眼中仲有國際法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n南海爭議單野 黑人問號"},{"pid":"4f34b27eaec995217eaa82f24556efe560b8a343","tid":630165,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T10:51:10.000Z","msg":"別拿法律當擋箭牌"},{"pid":"cba8d61515e546197abef6e31117aed928e46e86","tid":630165,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T12:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeed18cfe8a0e1a5d474054603787ae1a5eab4ac","tid":630165,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 汪汪"}]}